00045 // = 000-199 ===============================================================================//
00046 //
00047 // Reserve numerics 000-099 for server-client connections where the client
00048 // is local to the server. If any server is passed a numeric in this range
00049 // from another server then it is remapped to 100-199. -avalon
00050 //
